  "prompt": "What are the best international schools in Bangalore with the IGCSE Board?",
  "response": "Bangalore, often referred to as the Silicon Valley of India, is home to several prestigious international schools that offer the **IGCSE (International General Certificate of Secondary Education)** curriculum. Here are some of the best international schools in Bangalore with the IGCSE Board:\n\n### 1. **Inventure Academy**  \n   - **Curriculum**: IGCSE, ICSE, and IBDP  \n   - **Location**: Whitefield  \n   - Known for its holistic education approach, state-of-the-art facilities, and focus on extracurricular activities.\n\n### 2. **Canadian International School (CIS)**  \n   - **Curriculum**: IB (PYP, MYP, DP), IGCSE  \n   - **Location**: Yelahanka  \n   - Offers a global educational environment with a strong emphasis on academics, sports, and arts.\n\n### 3. **The International School Bangalore (TISB)**  \n   - **Curriculum**: IGCSE, IBDP  \n   - **Location**: Whitefield  \n   - One of the most renowned international schools in India, known for its academic excellence and world-class facilities.\n\n### 4. **Trio World School**  \n   - **Curriculum**: Cambridge IGCSE, IBDP  \n   - **Location**: Sahakara Nagar  \n   - Focuses on integrating technology with education and offers a multicultural environment.\n\n### 5. **Stonehill International School**  \n   - **Curriculum**: IB (PYP, MYP, DP), IGCSE  \n   - **Location**: Jala Hobli  \n   - A leading international school with an emphasis on fostering global citizenship and academic rigor.\n\n### 6. **Vidyashilp Academy**  \n   - **Curriculum**: CBSE, IGCSE, ICSE  \n   - **Location**: Yelahanka  \n   - Known for its innovative teaching methods and strong focus on student development.\n\n### 7. **Harvest International School**  \n   - **Curriculum**: Cambridge IGCSE, IBDP  \n   - **Location**: Sarjapur Road  \n   - Offers a balanced curriculum with a focus on academics, sports, and extracurricular activities.\n\n### 8. **Oakridge International School**  \n   - **Curriculum**: CBSE, IGCSE, IBDP  \n   - **Location**: Sarjapur Road  \n   - Part of the Nord Anglia Education group, known for its global learning opportunities and excellent facilities.\n\n### 9. **The Brigade School@Malleshwaram**  \n   - **Curriculum**: Cambridge IGCSE  \n   - **Location**: Malleshwaram  \n   - Offers a strong academic foundation with a focus on character development.\n\n### 10. **Ekya Schools**  \n   - **Curriculum**: CBSE, IGCSE  \n   - **Locations**: JP Nagar, ITPL, Byrathi  \n   - Focuses on personalized learning and skill development through a well-rounded curriculum.\n\n---\nThese schools are highly regarded for their academic rigor, extracurricular programs, and emphasis on holistic development. When selecting a school, consider factors such as location, facilities, teaching philosophy, and extracurricular offerings to find the best fit for your child.",
